{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Ban LGBTQIA+ conversion therapy",
        "additional_details": "We believe it has been proven to be ineffective, as citied on gov.uk: \u201cThere is no robust evidence that conversion therapy can achieve its stated therapeutic aim of changing sexual orientation or gender identity.\u201d The American Psychological Association also declared that conversion therapy is \u201cnot evidence-based therapy.\u201d",
        "background": "Ban the use of conversion therapy intended to change the sexual orientation or gender identity of members of the LGBTQIA+ community. We believe all forms of \u201cconversion therapy\u201d disrespect the equal moral value of LGBTQIA+ people and violate specific protected areas of liberty and equality.",
